---
import TopTitleLv2 from "./TopTitleLv2.astro";
import Button from "../common/Button.astro";
---

<section class="top-voice">
  <div class="l-container-s">
    <div class="l-section">
      <div class="top-voice-title-lv2">
        <TopTitleLv2
          title="生徒様の声"
          titleClass="c-top-title-lv2"
          titleImagePath="/assets/images/text/text-section-title-voice.svg"
          titleImageWidth="125"
          titleImageHeight="46"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="l-section-body">
        <ul class="top-voice-list">
          <li class="top-voice-item">
            <div class="top-voice-content">
              <h3 class="top-voice-title-lv3">子供の大きな成長を感じられる！</h3>
              <div class="top-voice-description">
                <p class="top-voice-text">子供と目を合わせながら、心で通じ合える感じがとても楽しかったです。<br>時には子供から指導が入ったり大きな成長を感じられるのは、親子フラならではだと思いました。<br>なかなか体を動かす機会もないので、とても良い運動になってると思います。</p>
                <span class="top-voice-name">A.Y.さん（親子フラ）</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="top-voice-illust">
              <img src="/assets/images/top/illust-top-voice-01.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="252" height="268">
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="top-voice-item">
            <div class="top-voice-content">
              <h3 class="top-voice-title-lv3">ハワイの音楽に触れ、親の私が癒やされています。</h3>
              <div class="top-voice-description">
                <p class="top-voice-text">娘がフラを習うようになってハワイの音楽に触れ、親の私が癒されています。<br>娘も年数を重ねる度に楽しくなってきてるようです♫</p>
                <span class="top-voice-name">C.S.さん（子供クラス）</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="top-voice-illust">
              <img src="/assets/images/top/illust-top-voice-02.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="252" height="268">
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="top-voice-item">
            <div class="top-voice-content">
              <h3 class="top-voice-title-lv3">毎回レッスンに行くのが本当に楽しみ！</h3>
              <div class="top-voice-description">
                <p class="top-voice-text">入会して間もないのですが、先生やお教室の皆さんがとても明るく、親切に接してくださいます。<br>毎回、レッスンに行くのが本当に楽しみです。</p>
                <span class="top-voice-name">M.K.さん（大人クラス）</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="top-voice-illust">
              <img src="/assets/images/top/illust-top-voice-03.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="252" height="268">
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="top-voice-btn">
          <Button
          buttonText="生徒様の声をもっと見る"
          buttonUrl="/voice"
        />
        </div>
      </div><!-- /.l-section-body -->
    </div><!-- /.l-section -->
  </div><!-- /.l-container-s -->
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../../styles/breakpoints' as *;

  .top-voice {
    background-image: url(/assets/images/top/bg-top-voice.webp);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center center;
  }

  .top-voice-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .top-voice-item {
    padding-block: 24px;
    padding-inline: 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-brown);
  }

  .top-voice-title-lv3 {
    color: var(--color-brown);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .top-voice-description {
    display: grid;
    gap: .5em;
    margin-block-start: 1em;
    line-height: 2;
  }

  .top-voice-name {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .top-voice-illust {
    display: none;
  }

  .top-voice-btn {
    margin-block-start: 64px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @include mq() {
    .top-voice-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 126px;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 40px;
      padding-block: 32px;
      padding-inline: 32px;
    }

    .top-voice-title-lv3 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .top-voice-illust {
      display: block;

      img {
        width: 126px;
      }
    }

    .top-voice-btn {
      margin-block-start: 80px;
    }
  }
</style>
